what you're carrying, so be it.

154
00:13:17,130 --> 00:13:19,214
But you don't have to
be a douche about it.

155
00:13:19,424 --> 00:13:21,925
Just told you what I'm carrying.

156
00:13:24,345 --> 00:13:27,097
So you're saying
you don't have a gun?

157
00:13:27,307 --> 00:13:28,932
Is that what you're saying?

158
00:13:29,142 --> 00:13:31,602
How are you here without a gun?

159
00:13:31,811 --> 00:13:34,271
- You have a gun?
- Yeah.

160
00:13:34,481 --> 00:13:37,483
Yeah. Of course. He's got a gun.

161
00:13:37,942 --> 00:13:40,444
I got at least two guns on me
that I'll tell you about.

162
00:13:40,653 --> 00:13:43,155
I go old school with
a Wilson Combat 1911.

163
00:13:43,364 --> 00:13:47,910
I got a Glock 22 Gen 3. And those are
just the ones I'll tell you about.

164
00:13:49,537 --> 00:13:52,748
I mean, what the hell? Really?

165
00:13:52,957 --> 00:13:55,250
How do you not pack a gun?

166
00:14:12,727 --> 00:14:16,104
Hi. Hello. My name is Price.

167
00:14:17,065 --> 00:14:19,107
Actually, that's not my name.

168
00:14:19,317 --> 00:14:23,904
But I have a nephew named Price.
I've always kind of liked that name.

169
00:14:24,113 --> 00:14:26,073
Anyway, we're not
dealing with names today.

170
00:14:26,282 --> 00:14:29,201
You can tell me or not tell me yours.
Or a fake one is fine.

171
00:14:30,203 --> 00:14:34,289
If I need to talk to you, I'd prefer
something other than "Hey, you."

172
00:14:35,458 --> 00:14:38,126
Either way, you all come highly
recommended, so thank you.

173
00:14:38,336 --> 00:14:41,380
First order of business,
we have a long drive ahead of us.

174
00:14:41,589 --> 00:14:44,466
I have a cooler of water in the car,
some soft drinks.

175
00:14:44,676 --> 00:14:48,470
I don't drink coffee,
but there is a diner on the corner.

176
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:53,475
Also a bathroom in there in case
you need to go before we go.

177
00:14:53,685 --> 00:14:55,727
Second order. Money.

178
00:14:55,937 --> 00:15:02,359
Just to be clear that the
agreed upon fee of $500 per man is...

179
00:15:02,569 --> 00:15:03,735
...agreed upon.

180
00:15:03,945 --> 00:15:05,779
- If that's acceptable...
- Yeah, I have a thought.

181
00:15:06,698 --> 00:15:07,739
Yeah.

182
00:15:07,949 --> 00:15:11,118
How about you give me
and Man Mountain 750 each?

183
00:15:11,327 --> 00:15:16,206
And send Uncle Fester there home.
He's not carrying a gun. He's useless.

184
00:15:17,125 --> 00:15:21,878
