need a gun to protect your employer.

187
00:15:28,720 --> 00:15:29,845
You're dead weight.

188
00:15:30,054 --> 00:15:32,889
- He's just a third wheel without a piece.
- I'll tell you what.

189
00:15:33,099 --> 00:15:35,434
If I need a gun, I'll use one of his.

190
00:15:35,643 --> 00:15:39,396
Really? One of my guns? How do you
picture that happening exactly?

191
00:15:39,606 --> 00:15:41,440
Well, I guess I'm gonna
take it from you.

192
00:15:41,649 --> 00:15:45,777
That... That is just special.

193
00:15:45,987 --> 00:15:48,947
Take. How are you gonna
take one of my guns?

194
00:15:49,157 --> 00:15:51,825
Come on, Billy Jackoff.

195
00:15:52,368 --> 00:15:54,494
Take my gun from me.

196
00:15:54,704 --> 00:15:56,246
Let me see it.

197
00:15:56,456 --> 00:16:00,042
Here. I'll make it easy for you.

198
00:16:05,173 --> 00:16:07,549
You can make it not so easy.

199
00:16:07,759 --> 00:16:09,676
Sure thing.

200
00:16:11,346 --> 00:16:12,763
You got it.

201
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,851
What the...? Son of a...

202
00:16:21,272 --> 00:16:24,858
Okay. Let's see what you got.

203
00:16:26,903 --> 00:16:30,906
Yeah. Yeah. Yeah. A guy like you...

204
00:16:31,115 --> 00:16:34,576
I'll bet you'd have an ankle holster,
wouldn't you?

205
00:16:34,786 --> 00:16:38,372
You know, that's cute. What else?

206
00:16:44,003 --> 00:16:47,923
Wow, now, that's impressive.

207
00:16:48,132 --> 00:16:51,218
So many guns,
I don't know which one to use.

208
00:16:51,427 --> 00:16:55,097
How about you? You want one?

209
00:17:01,979 --> 00:17:03,772
All right.

210
00:17:16,494 --> 00:17:17,744
Let's go.

211
00:17:17,954 --> 00:17:22,666
- But we need three guys.
- No. No, we don't. Come on. Let's go.

212
00:17:31,217 --> 00:17:33,427
Oh, he'll be fine.

213
00:17:33,636 --> 00:17:39,433
And now that I'm doing the job alone,
I get the full 1500. We agree upon that?

214
00:17:39,642 --> 00:17:41,017
Sure.

215
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:52,863
You got this, okay? No problem.

216
00:17:53,406 --> 00:17:54,448
Yes.

217
00:17:54,657 --> 00:17:57,701
- The suit okay? Is it too tight or too hot?
- Yeah.

218
00:17:57,910 --> 00:18:00,412
No, I mean. No. No. It's good.

219
00:18:00,621 --> 00:18:02,456
Well, you look good.

220
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,460
Can't even tell that's under there.

221
00:18:06,669 --> 00:18:08,253
It was a good idea.

222
00:18:08,463 --> 00:18:12,090
